{"tid":2350474,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"余文樂 NBA紀錄片","createTime":"2021-01-02T10:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T12:04:43.000Z","uid":230088,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c78600e3702fe4ba3fca6a309586b03df2d73bf6","tid":2350474,"uid":230088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T10:40:53.000Z","msg":"(以下內容由網友虛構製作，余文樂籃球真實水平並不能完全反映)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作為昔日NBA傳奇，曾經場均40分的籃球界巨人 &ndash; Fisherman Lok，雖然早已退隱球場加入演藝界，不過在Kobe Bryant退役後，湖人急需尋找一位球星，帶領紫金大軍重返榮耀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有一天，Kobe Bryant想起這位昔日的隊友，隨後在YouTube回顧了余文樂的籃球水平，默默點頭後，就立即邀請了Fisherman Lok加盟湖人。余文樂也是當仁不讓，毅然退出演藝界，承擔起這個重要的歷史任務。當余文樂重返NBA的消息經WOJ傳出後，可謂籃球界的一大震撼！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世間所有的相遇，都是久別重違，Fisherman Lok回歸讓籃球之神MJ亦不禁為之贊歎：「他就是世界上最好的籃球員！我以往從他身上學到了很多。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/uul/202101/210101/5fee887097ff11.25695745.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fuul%2F202101%2F210101%2F5fee887097ff11.25695745.jpg&h=2a3f0011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於Fisherman Lok的回歸，Michael Jordan也急不及待開記招<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFisherman Lok在湖人籃球訓練營大秀球技，用個人造詣震懾了所有人，才剛加盟湖人的LeBron James亦表示：「他X的！他怎樣做到的？」即使是聯盟第一人的LeBron James，在Fisherman Lok對比下也是微不足道，沒有比較就沒有傷害。在他的帶領下，湖人順利打入總決賽，並對陣速龍隊。在搶七大賽還剩下最後2.4秒之時，湖人仍然以121：123落後。<br />\n<br />\n面對如此危急存亡之事，速龍也是非常謹慎，Nick Nurse派出了五位球員包夾Fisherman Lok。Fisherman Lok雖然遭到對手所有人的招呼。不過對於這樣的防守，Fisherman Lok使出了生平第一次使用的絕技，幫助球隊成功絕殺速龍，拿下總冠軍！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/uul/202101/210101/5fee8c3ee61ca8.56771932.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fuul%2F202101%2F210101%2F5fee8c3ee61ca8.56771932.jpg&h=d3e8031a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在Fisherman Lok的魅力下，KD也願意底薪加盟湖人<br />\n<br />\n口講無憑，一起回顧《余文樂進軍NBA》實錄<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後條片笑到我抽筋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5RhyhLmQW9Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5RhyhLmQW9Y&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb01EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=a04d225c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5RhyhLmQW9Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://basketball.fanpiece.com/m/basketball-zone2/c1392325.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbasketball.fanpiece.com%2Fm%2Fbasketball-zone2%2Fc1392325.html&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb01EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=b39ea996\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://basketball.fanpiece.com/m/basketball-zone2/c1392325.html</a>"},{"pid":"de21ccdf46e76be607dd92012203f0f65c326795","tid":2350474,"uid":127579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T10:42:38.000Z","msg":"柏豪吊打啦"},{"pid":"2413d68f7f259c7844d7492521663dd44d1501f7","tid":2350474,"uid":28668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T10:44:21.000Z","msg":"重温經典未<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s9P1zx0vqlU&amp;lc=Ugitk2Q1lgRvYXgCoAEC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ds9P1zx0vqlU%26lc%3DUgitk2Q1lgRvYXgCoAEC&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb01EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=40e6ac2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s9P1zx0vqlU&amp;lc=Ugitk2Q1lgRvYXgCoAEC</a>"},{"pid":"a7ae728bb49722a9dab43c11e38d0d2d500d645d","tid":2350474,"uid":28668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T10:45:22.000Z","msg":"可惜揾唔到舊版"},{"pid":"691ee9f3b0bd77cdd5a4ee8bcbeed5f352de68e1","tid":2350474,"uid":111460,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T10:47:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-Hs5czRv9gk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-Hs5czRv9g